./my-claw/sdp/prd-r750-ollama-integration.md:22:| R750-008 | Implement fallback behavior: when Ollama is unhealthy, the agent selector automatically excludes it and falls back to cloud agents based on existing fitness scores. | MUST | T1 | - Unhealthy Ollama is excluded from candidate list<br/>- Cloud agents selected by existing fitness logic<br/>- Recovery: when Ollama returns healthy, it re-enters the candidate pool |
