./sdp/logs/Lead_T-004_20260408T223256Z_1775689515.log:842:./sdp/logs/Lead_T-001_20260408T223256Z_1775687592.log:2046:my-claw/tools/workspace/analysis_promptclaw_health.md:25:The daemon has its own parallel agent dispatch system (`run_agent()`) that duplicates the PromptClaw orchestrator's routing, verification, and retry logic. The core orchestrator (`promptclaw/orchestrator.py`) is never called from the daemon.
