./sdp/logs/Lead_T-003_20260408T223256Z_1775689060.log:1005:./my-claw/sdp/prd-proactive-intelligence.md:5:Five interconnected systems that transform CypherClaw from a reactive tool into a proactive, self-managing AI that maintains institutional memory, tracks its own costs, monitors project health, backs itself up, and carries context across sessions. CypherClaw should act autonomously on low-risk tasks (dep updates, security patches, prompt improvements) and ask before high-risk actions (deployments, deletions, architecture changes).
